trans-unit.source: Specifies the behaviors of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"></xref> object in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> control when the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"></xref> is clicked.
trans-unit.target: 동작을 지정는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"> </xref> 개체에 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"> </xref> 제어는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"> </xref> 를 클릭 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The HotSpotMode enumeration represents the behaviors that you can apply to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object within an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: HotSpotMode 열거형에 적용할 수 있는 동작을 나타냅니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>내에서 개체는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>컨트롤.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties use these enumeration values to set the behavior of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object when it is clicked.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성이 열거형 값을 사용 하 여 동작을 설정 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>클릭할 때 개체.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If both properties are set, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property specified on each individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object takes precedence over the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property on the control.
trans-unit.target: 두 속성 모두 설정 된 경우는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>각 개인에 지정 된 속성 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>개체 우선는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>컨트롤에서 속성.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `HotSpotMode.NotSet` for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of an individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> gets its behavior from the containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: 지정 하는 경우 `HotSpotMode.NotSet` 에 대 한는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>개인 속성 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>개체는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>포함 하는에서 해당 동작을 가져옵니다 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>컨트롤의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In this scenario, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A> property is either `NotSet` or no value is specified, the default behavior is to navigate to a URL.
trans-unit.target: 이 시나리오의 경우는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>컨트롤의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A>속성이 `NotSet` 또는 지정 된 값, URL을 탐색 하는 기본 동작입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control's behavior is not specified using either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> objects it contains, by default the behavior is `HotSpotMode.Navigate`.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 경우는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>컨트롤의 동작 중 하나를 사용 하 여 지정 하지 않으면는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성 또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성에는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>동작은 기본적으로 포함 개체 `HotSpotMode.Navigate`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: In addition, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> objects that an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control contains are set to `HotSpotMode.NotSet` and no value is specified for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, the default behavior is `HotSpotMode.Navigate`.
trans-unit.target: 또한 경우는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성에는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>개체는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>컨트롤 포함으로 설정 됩니다 `HotSpotMode.NotSet` 에 대 한 지정 된 값 및는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성을 기본 동작은 `HotSpotMode.Navigate`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `HotSpotMode.Navigate` for either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, the page navigates to a URL when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked.
trans-unit.target: 지정 하는 경우 `HotSpotMode.Navigate` 하나는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성 또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성, 페이지 URL을 탐색 때는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>를 클릭 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Image.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to specify the URL to navigate to.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Image.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성을 탐색할 URL을 지정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Image.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `HotSpotMode.PostBack` for either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, the page generates a postback to the server when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked.
trans-unit.target: 지정 하는 경우 `HotSpotMode.PostBack` 하나는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성 또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>페이지가 서버에 포스트백을 생성 때는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>를 클릭 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> property to specify a name for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>속성에 대 한 이름을 지정 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: This name will be passed in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs> event data when the postback event occurs.
trans-unit.target: 이 이름은에 전달 됩니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>포스트백 이벤트가 발생할 때 이벤트 데이터입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: When a postback <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: 다시 게시 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>를 클릭 하면는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>이벤트가 발생 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: To programmatically control the actions performed when a postback <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked, provide an event handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event.
trans-unit.target: 프로그래밍 방식으로 제어 하는 작업이 수행 다시 게시 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>는 클릭에 대 한 이벤트 처리기를 제공는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>이벤트.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `HotSpotMode.Inactive` for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object does not have any behavior when it is clicked.
trans-unit.target: 지정 하는 경우 `HotSpotMode.Inactive` 에 대 한는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성은 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>개체를 클릭할 때 동작을 수행 되어 있지 않습니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can use this value to create an inactive hot spot within a larger active hot spot.
trans-unit.target: 더 큰 active 핫 스폿 내 비활성 핫 스폿을 만들려는이 값을 사용할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: This option is provided to allow you to create more complex hot spot zones within an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: 내에서 더 복잡 한 핫 스폿 영역을 만들 수 있도록이 옵션은 제공 된 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>컨트롤.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: To create an inactive area within an active hot spot, you must specify the inactive hot spot before the active one in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: 에 현재 있는 하기 전에 비활성 핫 스폿을 지정 해야 하는 활성 핫 스폿 내 비활성 영역을 만들려면는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>컨트롤.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: For example, the following <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> defines an active ring by specifying an inactive circular hot spot within a larger active circular hot spot: ``` <asp:ImageMap ID="SaturnImage" ImageUrl="~/saturn.PNG" runat="server" OnClick="SaturnImage_Click"> <asp:CircleHotSpot AlternateText="planet" HotSpotMode=PostBack PostBackValue="planet" Radius=40 X=100 Y=100 /> <asp:CircleHotSpot HotSpotMode=Inactive Radius=60 X=100 Y=100 /> <asp:CircleHotSpot AlternateText="rings" HotSpotMode=PostBack PostBackValue="rings" Radius=80 X=100 Y=100 /> </asp:ImageMap> ```
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어, 다음 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>는 큰 활성 원형 핫 스폿 내 비활성 원형 핫 스폿을 지정 하 여 활성 링 정의: ``` <asp:ImageMap ID="SaturnImage" ImageUrl="~/saturn.PNG" runat="server" OnClick="SaturnImage_Click"> <asp:CircleHotSpot AlternateText="planet" HotSpotMode=PostBack PostBackValue="planet" Radius=40 X=100 Y=100 /> <asp:CircleHotSpot HotSpotMode=Inactive Radius=60 X=100 Y=100 /> <asp:CircleHotSpot AlternateText="rings" HotSpotMode=PostBack PostBackValue="rings" Radius=80 X=100 Y=100 /> </asp:ImageMap> ``` </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"> </xref> 모든 동작에는 없습니다.
